title: Located On Trinity River, Surrounded By Dining And Nightlife!
posting_body: ['Featuring spacious layouts with an abundance of natural light and ten unique floorplans, our gorgeous community has something to suit every personality.', 'Beautiful courtyards with serene fountains, private patios, and gorgeous hardwood floors.', 'Lounge beside our sparkling swimming pool, work up a sweat in our fully-equipped fitness center, and exploring the natural beauty of Trinity River and Trinity Trails.', 'Nestled beside the gorgeous banks of Clear Fork Trinity River and surrounded by a wide array of convenient shopping, dining, entertainment and nightlife options, everything you need is right at your fingertips at our pristine community.', "Plus, we're conveniently located near the I-30 freeway and only 10 minutes from the heart of the Dallas/Fort Worth area.", 'Please Call Desiree', 'show contact info', 'Mention Ad 408']
